    <p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.55pt;margin-left:-.25pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.5pt;line-height:111%;font-size:16px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;color:black;'>The foregoing licenses include, without limitation, the express rights to: (i) display or perform the art content underlying such Digital Asset(s) and collection content, on the Marketplace, a third party Marketplace, social media posts, blogs, editorials, advertising, market reports, virtual galleries, museums, virtual environments, editorials, or to the public; (ii) index the art content, and collection content in electronic databases, indexes, and catalogues; and (iii) host, store, distribute, and reproduce one or more copies of such art content and collection content within a distributed file keeping system, node cluster, or other database (e.g., IPFS) or cause, direct, or solicit others to do so. &nbsp; For purposes hereof, &ldquo;affiliate&rdquo; means an entity which, directly or indirectly, owns or controls, is owned or is controlled by or is under common ownership or control with Social Mint.</p>
